<?xml version="1.0"?>
<section xml:id="misc_polls">
  <title>Polls</title>
  <p>You can have a poll with a scale from x to y (such as 1 to 10).</p>
  <exercise runestone="pollid1"/>
  <hint>
    <program language="rst">
      <input>
.. poll:: pollid1
   :scale: 10
   :allowcomment:

    On a scale from 1 to 10, how important do you think it is to have a polling directive in the Runestone Tools?
</input>
    </program>
  </hint>
  <p>You can also have a poll with specific answers.</p>
  <exercise runestone="qstudent"/>
  <hint>
    <program language="rst">
      <input>
.. poll:: qstudent
   :option_1: student
   :option_2: teacher
   :option_3: other
   :option_4: prefer not to answer

   I am a :
</input>
    </program>
  </hint>
</section>
